1.Add new user
  adduser username
2.Delete use
  deluser username
3.Change password
  passwd username
4.Create a new group
  addgroup groupname
5.Add a user to the group
  usermod -a -G group_name username
6.Remove a group
  delgroup groupname
7.Remove a user
  gpasswd -d username groupname
8.List groups
  groups username
